тности свинден, еркшир, Англия, его отцу по имени Thurstan de Banastre V было 32 года, а матери, которую звали Cecilia de Lancaster, 20. Он женился на женщине по имени Lady Alice Mauleverer of Stoakes Hall, of Seend в местности свинден, еркшир, Англия, Великобритания. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын и 1 дочь. Он умер январь 1499 г. в местности Англия в возрасте 63 лет и был похоронен в местности Англия."},"sm":{"about 1437–January 1499":"e tusa o le 1437–Ianuari 1499","1437–1499":"1437–1499","1437–1500":"1437–1500","1446–Female":"1446–Ua Maliu","1463–Male":"1463–Ua Maliu","1464–1508":"1464–1508","1407–1442":"1407–1442","1419–1490":"1419–1490","13 January 1499":"13 Ianuari 1499","abt 1490":"e tusa o le 1490","1490":"1490","1437":"1437","1436":"1436","1446":"1446","1500":"1500","about 1437":"e tusa o le 1437","1455":"1455","1499":"1499","Abt 1442":"e tusa o le 1442","1464":"1464","1442":"1442","1463":"1463","January 1499":"Ianuari 1499","1508":"1508","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","Lancaster, Lancashire, England":"Lancaster, Lancashire, Egelani","Swinden, Craven, Yorkshire, England":"Swinden, Yorkshire, Egelani, United Kingdom","Preston, Lancashire, England":"Preston, Lancashire, Egelani","England":"Egelani","Swinden, Yorkshire, England":"Swinden, Yorkshire, Egelani","Y, Somme, Picardie, France":"Somme, Picardie, Farani"},"sk":{"about 1437–January 1499":"okolo 1437–január 1499","1437–1499":"1437–1499","1437–1500":"1437–1500","1446–Female":"1446–Zosnulá","1463–Male":"1463–Zosnulý","1464–1508":"1464–1508","1407–1442":"1407–1442","1419–1490":"1419–1490","13 January 1499":"13. január 1499","abt 1490":"okolo 1490","1490":"1490","1437":"1437","1436":"1436","1446":"1446","1500":"1500","about 1437":"okolo 1437","1455":"1455","1499":"1499","Abt 1442":"okolo 1442","1464":"1464","1442":"1442","1463":"1463","January 1499":"január 1499","1508":"1508","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","Lancaster, Lancashire, England":"Lancaster, Lancashire, England","Swinden, Craven, Yorkshire, England":"Sw